<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<title>Visitekaart</title>
<style>
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

@media (max-aspect-ratio: 9/16) {
  body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-image: url("https://64.media.tumblr.com/6f2206f3971ef3272ecaa8ce71d8f21e/tumblr_nuk6bbmkJb1smn4pqo5_1280.png");
  background-size: 130% auto ;
  }
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-image: url("https://64.media.tumblr.com/6f2206f3971ef3272ecaa8ce71d8f21e/tumblr_nuk6bbmkJb1smn4pqo5_1280.png");
  background-size: auto 130%;
}

/* Style the header */
header {
  color: #F1D6FA95;
  background-color: #b00b69;
  background: rgb(66, 10, 85);
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #4A1225 20%, rgb(66, 10, 85) 100%);
  padding: 0.625em; 
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 35px;
  color: white;
}
/* Style the "content" */
#content{
	position: relative;
	padding: 10% ;
	}
/* Create two columns/boxes that floats next to each other */
#bar {
  background: rgb(66, 10, 85);
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, #b00b6999 5%, #4A1225 20%);
  float: left;
  width: 20%;
  height: 300px;
  padding: 0em;
}
nav {
	position: absolute;
	flex-direction: row;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: flex-end;
	padding-left: 20%;
	transform: translateY(-50%);
}
a{
	color: white;
	}
a:visited{
	color: white;
	}


article {
  float: left;
  padding: 20px;
  width: 80%;
  background-color: #F1D6FA95;
  height: 300px;
}

/* Clear floats after the columns */
section::after {
  content: "";
  display: table;
  clear: both;
}

#profile {
	padding: 1.25em;
	position: absolute;
	}
#profile img {
  position: relative;
  background: url(https://nyathene.github.io/your-tribe-profile-card/assets/Squad1G-Athene.JPG) no-repeat;
  background-size: 10em;
  
  top: 0rem;
  width: 10em;
  height: auto;
  border: 5px solid #fff;
  border-radius: 10em;
  box-shadow: 0 0 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  transition: .25s .15s;
}
#profile img:hover {
  background: url(https://nyathene.github.io/your-tribe-profile-card/assets/Katdans.gif) no-repeat;
  background-size: 10em;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id=content>

        <div id=profile>
      <img src="" alt="" width="800" height="800">
		</div>
<header>
  <h2>Athene Guanipa</h2>
</header>

<section>
  <section  id=bar>
  </section>
 <nav>
	<ul>
		<a href="#Skills"><button>Skills</button></a>
		<a href="#Hobby"><button>Hobby's</button></a>
		<a href="#afkomst"><button>Afkomst</button></a>
 </nav>
  <article style="overflow-y:scroll;">
	<br><h2 id=Skills>Skills</h2>
	<p>Muziek</p>
	<p>Microsoft Office (ondanks dat ik die programma's niet heel fijn vind)</p><br>
    <br><h2 id=Hobby>Hobby's</h2>
    <p>Haken / crochet</p>
	<img src="assets/Crochet.png" alt="Amogus" width="auto" height="200">
	<img src="assets/Meowboy Hat.png" alt="Cowboy hoed met kattenoortjes" width="auto" height="200"><br>
	<p>Visuele kunst</p>
	<img src="assets/Shark painting.jpg" alt="Schilderij van twee haaien" width="auto" height="200"><br>
    <p>Saxofoon</p><br>
	
	<br><h2 id=afkomst>Afkomst</h2>
      <p>Geboren in 2003 in NL <img src="assets/NL Flag Pixel Arts.png" height="15em">, met een Surinaamse <img src="assets/Su Flag Pixel Arts.png" height="15em"> moeder en een Curaçaosche <img src="assets/Cura Flag Pixel Arts.png" height="15em"> vader.<br> in 2008 verhuisd naar Curaçao <img src="assets/Cura Flag Pixel Arts.png" height="15em"> <br> in 2022 terug verhuisd naar NL <img src="assets/NL Flag Pixel Arts.png" height="15em"> 	 </p>
      
  </article>
</section>
</div>
</body>
</html>

